dc_description_s: This data represents parks for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2023.[The County Lands layer for Washburn County is intended to represent County Lands referenced in the taxroll as described in legal descriptions and surveys. The polygons were extracted from the Tax Parcel polygons utilizing ownership information from the Tax Roll.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.washburn.wi.us/departments/land-info-surveyor-mapping/gis-data
